    └──2-b2b/
        ├──postman-struct/
        ├──postman-jobs/
        ├──sql-struct/
        └──sql-data/
```

---

# Merge Order

## B2C

```
0-both
+
1-b2c
```

## B2B

```
0-both
+
2-b2b
```

The **0-both** folder is always processed first.

